{"id":7785,"date":"2012-10-05T20:52:14","date_gmt":"2012-10-06T00:52:14","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=7785"},"modified":"2021-04-27T14:09:39","modified_gmt":"2021-04-27T10:09:39","slug":"charity-due-every-muslim","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/charity-due-every-muslim\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Charity is a duty upon every Muslim"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Charity is a duty upon every Muslim<\/strong>.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he has nothing?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Then he should work with his hands to benefit himself and give in charity.<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he cannot do so?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Then he should help a depressed, needy person.<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he cannot do so?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Then he should enjoin goodness and virtue<\/strong>.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he cannot do so?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Then he should refrain from evil, for that will be his charity<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6022, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1008<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u00a0\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e <stron